Texe Marrs - Mystery Mark of the New Age - Satan's Design for World Domination

'This explosive book exposes the darkness of the New Age Movement and uncovers Satan's bold design for world domination. Mystery Mark of the New Age fully reveals Satan's sobering Plan to give every man, woman, and child his unholy Mark. Yet the book ends on a note of triumph for all believing Christians--the glorious hope for our Lord's return.'
